Placeholder: The Drowning Post
[trigger none]

A placeholder encounter for the Drowning Post arc.

choices:

* Explore = Search the post [requires meets cunning 5]
    @if check combat medium {
        You find something valuable.
        +add_item knotwork_seed
        +finish_dungeon
    } @else {
        It doesn't go well.
        +add_condition injured
        +finish_dungeon
    }

* Negotiate = Talk your way through [requires meets cunning 5]
    @if check negotiation medium {
        You find something valuable.
        +add_item knotwork_seed
        +finish_dungeon
    } @else {
        It doesn't go well.
        +add_condition injured
        +finish_dungeon
    }

* Depart = Leave this place behind
    You depart Drowning Post.
    +flee_dungeon
